{"tid":2127044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒發現查奧爾比賽中搽「印度神油」","createTime":"2020-07-27T06:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T08:29:15.000Z","uid":103207,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"86989674bf4599624e072bbb0ab7663371e315fe","tid":2127044,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/07/27/f/f73efc9be4732662b3134c1215041426.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F07%2F27%2Ff%2Ff73efc9be4732662b3134c1215041426.jpg&h=dad30140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們只知道健美運動員會在身上擦油，沒想到足球運動員也會這麼做。<br />\n<br />\n  英媒曝光了阿達馬-查奧爾（Adama Traore）的一個小妙招：<span class=\"red\">比賽時候往身上塗潤滑油，這樣一來，就會讓對方防守球員很難抓住他</span>。在狼隊與水晶宮的比賽期間，也有眼尖的球迷看到了<span class=\"red\">教練組在場邊給他「上油」的一幕</span>。<br />\n<br />\n  人們經常形容靈活球員「像泥鰍一樣」，擦了油的查奧爾，那真就成了泥鰍了。<br />\n<br />\n  其實此舉也有些出於無奈，因為<span class=\"red\">查奧爾今季此前已經有4次在對抗中肩膀脫臼了</span>。最近的一次是在34輪與錫菲聯的比賽中，他開場2分鐘就在一次碰撞中脫臼，但硬是堅持了77分鐘才被換下。<br />\n<br />\n  再之前，他在對陣熱刺和曼聯時也有肩膀脫臼的情況。尤其是在和曼聯的比賽裡，麥佳亞（Harry Maguire）與他貼身纏鬥，查奧爾的臂部遭到拉拽，隨後痛苦倒地。<br />\n<br />\n  <span class=\"red\">因忌憚他的速度，所以防守球員經常會通過拉拽胳膊的方式來阻止查奧爾</span>，畢竟讓他衝起來威脅太大了，而<span class=\"red\">查奧爾本就脆弱的肩膀也經不住折騰，所以醫療團隊想出了這樣一個方法來保護他。下次再有人拉他隻手的時候，會發現好滑，根本拉不住</span>。"},{"pid":"3b4416b03bd5194862aa1e40d0dfe4ee55998258","tid":2127044,"uid":14983,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:45:13.000Z","msg":"對面球員隻手搽膠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50c88dd3659cabef6095b348f079ce185527e75","tid":2127044,"uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b4416b03bd5194862aa1e40d0dfe4ee55998258","tid":2127044,"uid":14983,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:45:13.000Z","msg":"對面球員隻手搽膠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"戴速龍手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbc48485919d63ee07ee7347db79141e38ab77a","tid":2127044,"uid":14719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:48:21.000Z","msg":"踢街場都有人會除晒衫成身汗衝埋黎<br />\n想食佢位都俾佢跣開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08107cd9202e9bb06547f414e56712f913c6f1d2","tid":2127044,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"搽落隻腳先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdd135560889ab57aa1863991f8e4a822ad3fae","tid":2127044,"uid":309814,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"DDG都有搽 不過係搽手掌"},{"pid":"0aa0915ab277f88754df819bddc4286c871b4c8b","tid":2127044,"uid":103207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3bdd135560889ab57aa1863991f8e4a822ad3fae","tid":2127044,"uid":309814,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"DDG都有搽 不過係搽手掌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"唔怪得佢成日用腳救波,怪錯牠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdc5489ad1bb11639f975470ef3781d1123ff59","tid":2127044,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bbc48485919d63ee07ee7347db79141e38ab77a","tid":2127044,"uid":14719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:48:21.000Z","msg":"踢街場都有人會除晒衫成身汗衝埋黎<br />\n想食佢位都俾佢跣開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:39:01.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf841cda932ea29f9e582f994ed65fee72a8101","tid":2127044,"uid":40765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0aa0915ab277f88754df819bddc4286c871b4c8b","tid":2127044,"uid":103207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3bdd135560889ab57aa1863991f8e4a822ad3fae","tid":2127044,"uid":309814,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,